## SECTION 3 — ABSOLUTE NON-NEGOTIABLES

These rules are absolute. Breaking any of them requires explicit approval
from Bashara before proceeding:

### Never Do
```
❌ Use `any` in TypeScript — ever
❌ Use <img> tag — always next/image
❌ Hardcode Indonesian/English strings in components — use next-intl
❌ Use float for monetary values — always integer IDR
❌ Deduct stock before Midtrans settlement webhook
